                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 422.11G93/818.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Hartman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-10-28T10:00:00-05:14">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 28, 1915—10 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s October 23, 4 p.m. Preliminary negotiations have resulted in fixing
                    November 4 for first conference at which nature and scope of proposed settlement
                    may be determined. Cannot advise until further notice.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
